div.div: Analysis of variance in red sea urchin fishing effort and landings.
div.p: (a) Mean total effort (number of receipts) and total landings (thousands of kg) during 2009â€“2011 per management season (months with 4-day work weeks [ limited access] and months with no management restrictions [ unlimited access]) and region (14 CDFW blocks within the Channel Islands [CI] and the port of Fort Bragg [FB]), and one standard error (SE) are displayed. (b) Two-way ANOVA results testing the differences in commercial red sea urchin total effort and total landings, between management (mgmt.) seasons, and between the two regions.
